title: Bug 134040 - Row should not have page break property in Property Editor
OB: When setting pageBreak properties in the Property Editor, the row allows the page break property to be set, but it cannot be saved.
EB: The row should not allow the page break property to be set in the Property Editor.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Open the Property Editor.
2. Navigate to the row settings.
3. Attempt to set the page break property for the row.
4. Notice that the row accepts the page break property, but when trying to save, the setting is not applied.
